```{r setup, include=FALSE}
library(xlsx)
library(car)
Uninsured <- readxl::read_xlsx("UninsuredState.xlsx")
```

```{r}
head(Uninsured)
Uninsured$`% High Income` = Uninsured$`% HIU Income 400% FPL` /  (Uninsured$`% HIU Income 100-138% FPL` + Uninsured$`% HIU Income 139-249% FPL` + Uninsured$`% HIU Income 250-400% FPL` + Uninsured$`% HIU Income < 100% FPL` + Uninsured$`% HIU Income 400% FPL`)
```

```{r}
mod1 = lm(Uninsured$`Percent Uninsured`~Uninsured$`% Married`)
mod2 = lm(Uninsured$`Percent Uninsured`~Uninsured$`% College Grad`)
mod3 = lm(Uninsured$`Percent Uninsured`~ Uninsured$`% Child in Family`)
```

```{r}
mod4 = lm(Uninsured$`Percent Uninsured`~Uninsured$`% High Income`)
summary(mod4)
```
